{"tid":258223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家大學生畢完業人工咁低係好正常","createTime":"2017-05-26T02:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T12:16:05.000Z","uid":79481,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c594a4d90907f5a045d4433bbc4421b0280062e","tid":258223,"uid":79481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:07:52.000Z","msg":"唔好腐皮住 聽埋我講先<br />\n<br />\n最主要既原因係依家大學生太多<br />\n<br />\n通街都係大學生 i大又話自己大學生<br />\n<br />\n外國野雞又話自己大學生<br />\n<br />\n搞到有d供過於求<br />\n<br />\n又或者可以話大學生根本就係基本要求<br />\n<br />\n長久之 好快大學張沙紙就變得唔值錢<br />\n<br />\n要人工高就要學其他人地無既野<br />\n<br />\n所以大學生人工咁低根本就係好正常既事<br />\n<br />\n同買野既道理一樣"},{"pid":"6bbab7da7d25d2de574cf65ef2ab8fe77321c1d9","tid":258223,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:12:28.000Z","msg":"唔洗番工既大學生呢?"},{"pid":"20885df9dc792a4c086b25f7a752c647587934a4","tid":258223,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗番工既大學生呢?</blockquote><br />\n好似你咁得閒咩"},{"pid":"83332dfaa30e8c1414722eb33733164a556fd89e","tid":258223,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"咁見工條友唔識睇佢邊間大學咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d411e7d3e4e7f49008291bd2107359aec0fb81","tid":258223,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁見工條友唔識睇佢邊間大學咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係勁既大學 你唔洗同佢擔心喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁既大學都要睇埋邊科喇"},{"pid":"9da904a3ee524979d273b87db455dfa1c8750ce9","tid":258223,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔洗番工既大學生呢?</blockquote><br />\n好似你咁得閒咩</blockquote><br />\n我諗係未訓醒ja掛"},{"pid":"6cacc06f35c660545ba469ca313d0727ca4233ce","tid":258223,"uid":